<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><meta charset="utf-8"><title>Security Alert</title></head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="background: #e65100; padding: 16px; border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0;">
    <h2 style="color: white; margin: 0;">🚨 Security Alert — Immediate Action Required</h2>
  </div>
  <div style="border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; padding: 24px; border-radius: 0 0 4px 4px;">
    <p>Dear {{employeeName}},</p>
    <p>We have detected a potential security breach affecting your account. Your credentials may have been compromised in a recent data incident.</p>
    <p>Please verify your identity immediately to secure your account and prevent unauthorized access.</p>
    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;">
      <a href="{{trackingUrl}}" style="background: #e65100; color: white; padding: 12px 32px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">
        Verify My Identity
      </a>
    </div>
    <p style="color: #666; font-size: 12px;">Security Operations Center | {{organizationName}}</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>